    <title>Ubuntu root用户下java -version无法获取java环境变量解决办法</title>
    <link>http://example.org/ubuntu-root%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E4%B8%8Bjava-version%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96java%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95/</link>
